ld''' is a type of [[shield]] that appears in ''[[dNetHack]]'', ''[[SpliceHack]]'', and ''[[Hack'EM]]''. It provides [[AC]] 3 when worn.\n\nIn [[dNetHack]] the tower shield provides 4AC (and 0 DR, like all shields), and grants [[Magic cancellation|MC1]].\n\n== Strategy ==\n\nThe tower shield provides the most AC of any shield, but unfortunately it also weighs the most. It also inhibits spellcasting like other metallic shields.\n\n==References==\n<references/><!--{{variant-36x}}-->\n[[Category:Shields]]\n[[Category:dNetHack]]\n[[Category:SpliceHack]]\n[[Category:Hack'EM]]"}